  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Overall Objective: Increase transparency and accountability in implementation of projects across Kinshasa, South and North Kivu.

Specific objectives:
1. Promoting students engagement to increase transparency and accountability in implementation of projects; 
2. Promoting dialogue between students, service users, government bodies, and projects implementing agencies.
3. Promoting the use of social accountability approaches by citizen, local civil society organizations and governments to make project implementation more effective and efficient.;</narrative>
